description: Demolition of remaining buildings and structures and erection of a 67 storey building (240.545m AOD) with two basement levels, comprising 861 residential units (Use Class C3), 942sqm (GIA) flexible commercial floorspace (Use Class A1-A3 and D2), ancillary circulation space and plant, as well as associated infrastructure, public realm and parking. Accompanied by an Environmental Impact Statement.
